&lt;h3&gt;


Your Next Steps
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Start simple:&lt;/strong&gt; Add 2-3 languages to your current project&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Get feedback:&lt;/strong&gt; Ask users if they'd use other languages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Iterate:&lt;/strong&gt; Add languages based on demand, not assumptions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Measure:&lt;/strong&gt; Track engagement by language&lt;/li&gt;
